1.plot: Welcome to the world of FML Series! "F.M.L." ("F**k My Life"), is a comedic web series about five millennial friends of color navigating through the bullshit called life as they try to find themselves, their identity, actual money in their bank account, their purpose and make sure to drink a lot and get laid along the way.

locations: New York City, New York, USA::(on location)
imdb.plot outline: Working in porn, quarter-life crises, five friends; welcome to our world. Sex is their drug and pain is their love. An erotica writer, an indie filmmaker turned porn director, an actor/model turned aspiring porn star, a sex store employee and entrepreneur of sex make up the group of friends. As millennials, they navigate through life trying to find a purpose, money, a good lay and identity while partying their sorrows away. This prime age of self-discovery and doubt is the reason this group of broken and sexually curious people have found one another.
